# p1cli_python

Core module for resolving and loading Python packages from `.venv`.

## Package resolution logic

- If package == "p1cli" or starts with "p1cli.", look in src/p1cli
- Otherwise, use uv tree to find packages, fall back to site-packages scan
- Supports both directory modules (polars.series) and file modules (fastapi.cli)

## Special cases

- Submodules with dots: "polars.dataframe" → find "polars" then "dataframe" subdir
- File modules: "fastapi.cli" → look for "cli.py" inside fastapi package

## Dev mode

When working on p1cli itself, it resolves from src/ without needing .venv
